[{"Code":"en","Title":"Wix","Slug":"wix","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mdeaitxi-9dohm4-040\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mdeaixej-wemmtc-042\">Supported only for ID and PH businesses.</p></div></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"8e30dc29-ef36-4dd1-a859-77c235c72923\">Wix is a cloud-based web development platform that lets users create HTML5 websites and mobile sites using drag-and-drop tools. Its eCommerce system allows you to sell a wide range of products with easy setup.</p><p data-block-id=\"11f65338-b688-4330-ba91-8f757891e511\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Follow this guideline to start integrating Xendit with your Wix platform.</span></p><h2 data-block-id=\"e77de5e0-32e7-4737-92fb-55ee080db2d9\"><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><p data-block-id=\"837f458a-2c82-4b38-922b-404ed5e28531\">Before integrating Xendit with Wix, ensure the following:</p><ol data-block-id=\"24f934a7-22e0-4171-864c-58a06646215d\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"ff9c27f0-82dd-49fe-9fb0-b826e6c97d3a\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"1ccb1494-4293-44d4-aea9-1135461264bf\"><strong>Xendit Registration</strong>:</p><ul data-block-id=\"30aac4ad-058c-4a20-91ae-13cb766f8984\"><li data-block-id=\"670abe8a-1696-42e4-822a-174b77497682\"><p data-block-id=\"f20b79d8-1590-4318-8dbc-c16ffdd05888\">Register with Xendit to obtain your <strong>test</strong> and <strong>live API keys</strong>.</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"802f0038-4b38-48f3-8706-d2d715447685\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f098ff21-250d-4b20-b4ed-38ac4ae37119\"><strong>Wix Account</strong>:</p><ul data-block-id=\"dc812e5f-d0ba-4613-98c5-93d652041585\"><li data-block-id=\"4927be29-eabf-4bd6-b229-521d58658570\"><p data-block-id=\"37257cee-b61d-4601-8199-d26c7b86b1d4\">Sign up for Wix and subscribe to the <strong>Business Plan</strong> or <strong>eCommerce Plan</strong> package.</p></li></ul></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"77c34e23-7b5d-4d0c-9576-d05b03ecd09f\">Installation</h2><p style=\"text-align:start;\" data-block-id=\"c758a8ad-3ccb-489c-bbdb-a585e63e8bdf\">Here are the steps you need to do to integrate Xendit and your Wix store:</p><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-pan-x:;--tw-pan-y:;--tw-pinch-zoom:;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ordinal:;--tw-slashed-zero:;--tw-numeric-figure:;--tw-numeric-spacing:;--tw-numeric-fraction:;--tw-ring-inset:;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;--tw-blur:;--tw-brightness:;--tw-contrast:;--tw-grayscale:;--tw-hue-rotate:;--tw-invert:;--tw-saturate:;--tw-sepia:;--tw-drop-shadow:;--tw-backdrop-blur:;--tw-backdrop-brightness:;--tw-backdrop-contrast:;--tw-backdrop-grayscale:;--tw-backdrop-hue-rotate:;--tw-backdrop-invert:;--tw-backdrop-opacity:;--tw-backdrop-saturate:;--tw-backdrop-sepia:;color:rgb(55, 65, 81);font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\"><p data-block-id=\"0135620c-4522-4739-b3a0-b9e3dd679aa3\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cCGLfNHxocg\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"YouTube video player\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;display:flex;vertical-align:middle;height:315px;width:560px;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\"></iframe></p><ol data-block-id=\"4edcfcc2-87e2-42c4-9930-a8a774d30cc0\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"553418c5-3cdb-4b71-862a-44b06de50ee8\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"e83a7d5a-f5bd-4276-8f13-aeef9ea19a83\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Go to&nbsp;<em>Setting &gt; Accept Payments</em>&nbsp;in your Wix dashboard and choose \"Online Payments by Xendit\" in&nbsp;<strong>More Payment Options</strong>, click Connect</span></p></li><li data-block-id=\"681b44be-e24a-4896-a541-f18ccdbc2291\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"dea0657c-3d99-4843-a9e7-ee99ca3eb2ee\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Input Xendit API key to the <strong>Secret Key</strong> field in your Wix dashboard Xendit setting</span></p><ol data-block-id=\"35c2b5ee-3d5d-4a1b-83b7-f7dd677fdd89\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"ad90b9fc-5805-4e11-be8d-7c71a190e662\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"0721e3b3-f894-48e1-821c-31893cce38e8\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">To process test transaction, please input Secret Key from Xendit Dashboard in Test environment</span></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ec06ecd8-9909-4682-ad06-f79e7344711d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"907d54e3-b9c5-4f86-9fe4-3c5d5ead9611\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">To process real transaction, please input Secret Key from Xendit Dashboard in Live environment</span></p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"b984c9ca-5e36-4219-aaed-14f585aeb67d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"08a2bf74-1724-4b50-a96f-163da6eb269a\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Click&nbsp;<strong>Connect</strong></span></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"905731a3-899d-476d-917b-2131cc1486d0\">Payment Flow</h2></div><p data-block-id=\"4e836cf6-2b71-4008-a8aa-4513ec827182\"><img data-block-id=\"mdeaicnu-rowc4q-039\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Wix Payment Flow VA.gif\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"\"></p><p data-block-id=\"c096e0ff-00dd-47f1-a7b2-d9c729ff6bfb\"></p><p data-block-id=\"dd6af337-74a9-4b3e-bfdf-ede64e0f98bf\"></p><br type=\"block\"><p data-block-id=\"d5c01066-852b-4beb-9098-3527ef7ec420\"></p><p data-block-id=\"eb3b3afc-8e4e-422f-98b9-0dd8ff928024\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Wix","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Wix","Slug":"wix","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5q-8uueok-409\">Wix adalah platform pengembangan web berbasis cloud yang memungkinkan pengguna membuat situs web HTML5 dan situs seluler menggunakan alat seret dan lepas. Sistem eCommerce-nya memungkinkan Anda menjual berbagai macam produk dengan pengaturan yang mudah.</p><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5q-icnbji-410\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Ikuti panduan ini untuk mulai mengintegrasikan Xendit dengan platform Wix Anda.</span></p><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs33s5r-sli5y6-411\"><strong>Persyaratan</strong></h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5r-qz1x7j-412\">Sebelum mengintegrasikan Xendit dengan Wix, pastikan hal berikut:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mcs33s5r-bws7sg-413\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs33s5r-y7j6zh-414\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-rpamnh-415\"><strong>Pendaftaran Xendit</strong>:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-ayedlm-416\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-1qw3fn-417\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-ciq523-418\">Daftar dengan Xendit untuk mendapatkan <strong>kunci pengujian</strong> dan <strong>API langsung</strong> Anda.</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-cjcxko-419\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-1m7op8-420\"><strong>Akun Wix</strong>:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-8mx8kl-421\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-ddpa77-422\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-z63jes-423\">Daftar ke Wix dan berlangganan paket <strong>Paket Bisnis</strong> atau <strong>Paket eCommerce</strong> .</p></li></ul></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-wguref-424\">Instalasi</h2><p style=\"text-align:start;\" data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-siygp7-425\">Berikut adalah langkah-langkah yang perlu Anda lakukan untuk mengintegrasikan Xendit dan toko Wix Anda:</p><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-pan-x:;--tw-pan-y:;--tw-pinch-zoom:;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ordinal:;--tw-slashed-zero:;--tw-numeric-figure:;--tw-numeric-spacing:;--tw-numeric-fraction:;--tw-ring-inset:;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;--tw-blur:;--tw-brightness:;--tw-contrast:;--tw-grayscale:;--tw-hue-rotate:;--tw-invert:;--tw-saturate:;--tw-sepia:;--tw-drop-shadow:;--tw-backdrop-blur:;--tw-backdrop-brightness:;--tw-backdrop-contrast:;--tw-backdrop-grayscale:;--tw-backdrop-hue-rotate:;--tw-backdrop-invert:;--tw-backdrop-opacity:;--tw-backdrop-saturate:;--tw-backdrop-sepia:;color:rgb(55, 65, 81);font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5s-wmwryb-426\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cCGLfNHxocg\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"YouTube video player\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;display:flex;vertical-align:middle;height:315px;width:560px;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\"></iframe></p><ol data-block-id=\"mcs33s5t-t9xykg-427\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs33s5t-n6xeqm-428\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5t-vtsyla-429\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Buka <em>Pengaturan &gt; Terima Pembayaran</em> di dasbor Wix Anda dan pilih \"Pembayaran Online oleh Xendit\" di <strong>Opsi Pembayaran Lainnya</strong>, klik Hubungkan</span></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs33s5t-mvhahd-430\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5t-me6a6l-431\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Masukkan kunci API Xendit ke bidang <strong>Kunci Rahasia</strong> di pengaturan Xendit dasbor Wix Anda</span></p><ol data-block-id=\"mcs33s5t-2hf4xy-432\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs33s5t-vwmhnu-433\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5t-6pjzuz-434\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Untuk memproses transaksi pengujian, silahkan masukkan Kunci Rahasia dari Dashboard Xendit di lingkungan pengujian</span></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs33s5t-g4m41t-435\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5t-blu36a-436\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Untuk memproses transaksi nyata, silahkan masukkan Kunci Rahasia dari Dashboard Xendit di lingkungan Live</span></p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs33s5u-ouj5h4-437\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5u-o2c80d-438\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Klik <strong>Hubungkan</strong></span></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs33s5u-sk9m0c-439\">Alur Pembayaran</h2></div><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5u-ecz936-440\"><img data-block-id=\"mcs33s5u-0nuhe1-441\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(98).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(98).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5u-qoxrsz-442\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5u-m2cl5i-443\"></p><br type=\"block\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5u-49jyi5-444\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs33s5u-zwyi93-445\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Wix","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Wix","Slug":"wix","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mdeaitxi-9dohm4-040\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mdeaixej-wemmtc-042\">รองรับเฉพาะธุรกิจใน ID และ PH เท่านั้น</p></div></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"8e30dc29-ef36-4dd1-a859-77c235c72923\">Wix เป็นแพลตฟอร์มพัฒนาเว็บไซต์บนคลาวด์ที่ช่วยให้ผู้ใช้สามารถสร้างเว็บไซต์ HTML5 และเว็บไซต์สำหรับมือถือได้โดยใช้เครื่องมือแบบลากและวาง (drag-and-drop) ระบบ eCommerce ของ Wix ช่วยให้คุณสามารถขายสินค้าได้หลากหลายประเภทด้วยการตั้งค่าที่ง่ายดาย</p><p data-block-id=\"11f65338-b688-4330-ba91-8f757891e511\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">ทำตามคำแนะนำนี้เพื่อเริ่มต้นการเชื่อมต่อ Xendit เข้ากับแพลตฟอร์ม Wix ของคุณ</span></p><h2 data-block-id=\"e77de5e0-32e7-4737-92fb-55ee080db2d9\"><strong>ข้อกำหนดเบื้องต้น</strong></h2><p data-block-id=\"837f458a-2c82-4b38-922b-404ed5e28531\">ก่อนที่จะเชื่อมต่อ Xendit กับ Wix โปรดตรวจสอบให้แน่ใจว่าคุณมีสิ่งต่อไปนี้:</p><ol data-block-id=\"24f934a7-22e0-4171-864c-58a06646215d\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"ff9c27f0-82dd-49fe-9fb0-b826e6c97d3a\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"1ccb1494-4293-44d4-aea9-1135461264bf\"><strong>การลงทะเบียน Xendit</strong>:</p><ul data-block-id=\"30aac4ad-058c-4a20-91ae-13cb766f8984\"><li data-block-id=\"670abe8a-1696-42e4-822a-174b77497682\"><p data-block-id=\"f20b79d8-1590-4318-8dbc-c16ffdd05888\">ลงทะเบียนกับ Xendit เพื่อรับ <strong>test</strong> และ <strong>live API keys</strong> ของคุณ</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"802f0038-4b38-48f3-8706-d2d715447685\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f098ff21-250d-4b20-b4ed-38ac4ae37119\"><strong>บัญชี Wix</strong>:</p><ul data-block-id=\"dc812e5f-d0ba-4613-98c5-93d652041585\"><li data-block-id=\"4927be29-eabf-4bd6-b229-521d58658570\"><p data-block-id=\"37257cee-b61d-4601-8199-d26c7b86b1d4\">สมัคร Wix และสมัครแพ็กเกจ <strong>Business Plan</strong> หรือ <strong>eCommerce Plan</strong></p></li></ul></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"77c34e23-7b5d-4d0c-9576-d05b03ecd09f\">การติดตั้ง</h2><p style=\"text-align:start;\" data-block-id=\"c758a8ad-3ccb-489c-bbdb-a585e63e8bdf\">นี่คือขั้นตอนที่คุณต้องทำเพื่อเชื่อมต่อ Xendit กับร้านค้า Wix ของคุณ:</p><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-pan-x:;--tw-pan-y:;--tw-pinch-zoom:;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ordinal:;--tw-slashed-zero:;--tw-numeric-figure:;--tw-numeric-spacing:;--tw-numeric-fraction:;--tw-ring-inset:;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;--tw-blur:;--tw-brightness:;--tw-contrast:;--tw-grayscale:;--tw-hue-rotate:;--tw-invert:;--tw-saturate:;--tw-sepia:;--tw-drop-shadow:;--tw-backdrop-blur:;--tw-backdrop-brightness:;--tw-backdrop-contrast:;--tw-backdrop-grayscale:;--tw-backdrop-hue-rotate:;--tw-backdrop-invert:;--tw-backdrop-opacity:;--tw-backdrop-saturate:;--tw-backdrop-sepia:;color:rgb(55, 65, 81);font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\"><p data-block-id=\"0135620c-4522-4739-b3a0-b9e3dd679aa3\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cCGLfNHxocg\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"YouTube video player\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;display:flex;vertical-align:middle;height:315px;width:560px;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\"></iframe></p><ol data-block-id=\"4edcfcc2-87e2-42c4-9930-a8a774d30cc0\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"553418c5-3cdb-4b71-862a-44b06de50ee8\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"e83a7d5a-f5bd-4276-8f13-aeef9ea19a83\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">ไปที่&nbsp;<em>Setting &gt; Accept Payments</em>&nbsp;ใน Wix dashboard ของคุณ และเลือก \"Online Payments by Xendit\" ในส่วน&nbsp;<strong>More Payment Options</strong>, จากนั้นคลิก Connect</span></p></li><li data-block-id=\"681b44be-e24a-4896-a541-f18ccdbc2291\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"dea0657c-3d99-4843-a9e7-ee99ca3eb2ee\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">ป้อน Xendit API key ลงในช่อง <strong>Secret Key</strong> ในการตั้งค่า Xendit บน Wix dashboard ของคุณ</span></p><ol data-block-id=\"35c2b5ee-3d5d-4a1b-83b7-f7dd677fdd89\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"ad90b9fc-5805-4e11-be8d-7c71a190e662\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"0721e3b3-f894-48e1-821c-31893cce38e8\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">หากต้องการดำเนินการธุรกรรมทดสอบ โปรดป้อน Secret Key จาก Xendit Dashboard ใน Test environment</span></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ec06ecd8-9909-4682-ad06-f79e7344711d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"907d54e3-b9c5-4f86-9fe4-3c5d5ead9611\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">หากต้องการดำเนินการธุรกรรมจริง โปรดป้อน Secret Key จาก Xendit Dashboard ใน Live environment</span></p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"b984c9ca-5e36-4219-aaed-14f585aeb67d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"08a2bf74-1724-4b50-a96f-163da6eb269a\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">คลิก&nbsp;<strong>Connect</strong></span></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"905731a3-899d-476d-917b-2131cc1486d0\">ขั้นตอนการชำระเงิน</h2></div><p data-block-id=\"4e836cf6-2b71-4008-a8aa-4513ec827182\"><img data-block-id=\"mdeaicnu-rowc4q-039\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Wix Payment Flow VA.gif\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style></p><p data-block-id=\"c096e0ff-00dd-47f1-a7b2-d9c729ff6bfb\"></p><p data-block-id=\"dd6af337-74a9-4b3e-bfdf-ede64e0f98bf\"></p><br type=\"block\"><p data-block-id=\"d5c01066-852b-4beb-9098-3527ef7ec420\"></p><p data-block-id=\"eb3b3afc-8e4e-422f-98b9-0dd8ff928024\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Wix","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Wix","Slug":"wix","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mdeaitxi-9dohm4-040\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mdeaixej-wemmtc-042\">Compatible solo para comercios de ID y PH.</p></div></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"8e30dc29-ef36-4dd1-a859-77c235c72923\">Wix es una plataforma de desarrollo web basada en la nube que permite a los usuarios crear sitios web HTML5 y sitios móviles utilizando herramientas de arrastrar y soltar (drag-and-drop). Su sistema de eCommerce le permite vender una amplia gama de productos con una configuración sencilla.</p><p data-block-id=\"11f65338-b688-4330-ba91-8f757891e511\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Siga esta guía para comenzar a integrar Xendit con su plataforma Wix.</span></p><h2 data-block-id=\"e77de5e0-32e7-4737-92fb-55ee080db2d9\"><strong>Requisitos</strong></h2><p data-block-id=\"837f458a-2c82-4b38-922b-404ed5e28531\">Antes de integrar Xendit con Wix, asegúrese de lo siguiente:</p><ol data-block-id=\"24f934a7-22e0-4171-864c-58a06646215d\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"ff9c27f0-82dd-49fe-9fb0-b826e6c97d3a\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"1ccb1494-4293-44d4-aea9-1135461264bf\"><strong>Registro en Xendit</strong>:</p><ul data-block-id=\"30aac4ad-058c-4a20-91ae-13cb766f8984\"><li data-block-id=\"670abe8a-1696-42e4-822a-174b77497682\"><p data-block-id=\"f20b79d8-1590-4318-8dbc-c16ffdd05888\">Regístrese en Xendit para obtener sus <strong>API keys</strong> de <strong>prueba</strong> y <strong>en vivo</strong>.</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"802f0038-4b38-48f3-8706-d2d715447685\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f098ff21-250d-4b20-b4ed-38ac4ae37119\"><strong>Cuenta de Wix</strong>:</p><ul data-block-id=\"dc812e5f-d0ba-4613-98c5-93d652041585\"><li data-block-id=\"4927be29-eabf-4bd6-b229-521d58658570\"><p data-block-id=\"37257cee-b61d-4601-8199-d26c7b86b1d4\">Regístrese en Wix y suscríbase al paquete <strong>Business Plan</strong> o <strong>eCommerce Plan</strong>.</p></li></ul></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"77c34e23-7b5d-4d0c-9576-d05b03ecd09f\">Instalación</h2><p style=\"text-align:start;\" data-block-id=\"c758a8ad-3ccb-489c-bbdb-a585e63e8bdf\">Estos son los pasos que debe seguir para integrar Xendit y su tienda Wix:</p><div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-pan-x:;--tw-pan-y:;--tw-pinch-zoom:;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ordinal:;--tw-slashed-zero:;--tw-numeric-figure:;--tw-numeric-spacing:;--tw-numeric-fraction:;--tw-ring-inset:;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;--tw-blur:;--tw-brightness:;--tw-contrast:;--tw-grayscale:;--tw-hue-rotate:;--tw-invert:;--tw-saturate:;--tw-sepia:;--tw-drop-shadow:;--tw-backdrop-blur:;--tw-backdrop-brightness:;--tw-backdrop-contrast:;--tw-backdrop-grayscale:;--tw-backdrop-hue-rotate:;--tw-backdrop-invert:;--tw-backdrop-opacity:;--tw-backdrop-saturate:;--tw-backdrop-sepia:;color:rgb(55, 65, 81);font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;\"><p data-block-id=\"0135620c-4522-4739-b3a0-b9e3dd679aa3\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cCGLfNHxocg\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"YouTube video player\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px solid rgb(229, 231, 235);--tw-border-spacing-x:0;--tw-border-spacing-y:0;--tw-translate-x:0;--tw-translate-y:0;--tw-rotate:0;--tw-skew-x:0;--tw-skew-y:0;--tw-scale-x:1;--tw-scale-y:1;--tw-scroll-snap-strictness:proximity;--tw-ring-offset-width:0px;--tw-ring-offset-color:#fff;--tw-ring-color:rgba(59,130,246,.5);--tw-ring-offset-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-ring-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow:0 0 #0000;--tw-shadow-colored:0 0 #0000;display:flex;vertical-align:middle;height:315px;width:560px;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\"></iframe></p><ol data-block-id=\"4edcfcc2-87e2-42c4-9930-a8a774d30cc0\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"553418c5-3cdb-4b71-862a-44b06de50ee8\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"e83a7d5a-f5bd-4276-8f13-aeef9ea19a83\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Vaya a&nbsp;<em>Configuración > Aceptar Pagos</em>&nbsp;en su Dashboard de Wix y elija \"Online Payments by Xendit\" en&nbsp;<strong>Más Opciones de Pago</strong>, haga clic en Conectar.</span></p></li><li data-block-id=\"681b44be-e24a-4896-a541-f18ccdbc2291\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"dea0657c-3d99-4843-a9e7-ee99ca3eb2ee\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Ingrese la API key de Xendit en el campo <strong>Secret Key</strong> en la configuración de Xendit de su Dashboard de Wix.</span></p><ol data-block-id=\"35c2b5ee-3d5d-4a1b-83b7-f7dd677fdd89\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"ad90b9fc-5805-4e11-be8d-7c71a190e662\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"0721e3b3-f894-48e1-821c-31893cce38e8\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Para procesar una Transacción de prueba, por favor, ingrese la Secret Key de su Xendit Dashboard en el entorno de prueba.</span></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ec06ecd8-9909-4682-ad06-f79e7344711d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"907d54e3-b9c5-4f86-9fe4-3c5d5ead9611\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Para procesar una Transacción real, por favor, ingrese la Secret Key de su Xendit Dashboard en el entorno en vivo.</span></p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"b984c9ca-5e36-4219-aaed-14f585aeb67d\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><p data-block-id=\"08a2bf74-1724-4b50-a96f-163da6eb269a\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);\" type=\"spanMark\">Haga clic en&nbsp;<strong>Conectar</strong></span></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"905731a3-899d-476d-917b-2131cc1486d0\">Flujo de Pago</h2></div><p data-block-id=\"4e836cf6-2b71-4008-a8aa-4513ec827182\"><img data-block-id=\"mdeaicnu-rowc4q-039\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Wix Payment Flow VA.gif\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style></p><p data-block-id=\"c096e0ff-00dd-47f1-a7b2-d9c729ff6bfb\"></p><p data-block-id=\"dd6af337-74a9-4b3e-bfdf-ede64e0f98bf\"></p><br type=\"block\"><p data-block-id=\"d5c01066-852b-4beb-9098-3527ef7ec420\"></p><p data-block-id=\"eb3b3afc-8e4e-422f-98b9-0dd8ff928024\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Wix","Description":null}]